premise_source_doc_sentence: The band formed when self-taught musician Hubert Winston McIntosh  (  Peter Tosh  )  met Neville Livingston  (  Bunny Wailer  )  , and Robert Nesta Marley  (  Bob Marley  )  in 1963 and taught them how to play guitar , keyboards , and percussion .
